        "timestamp": "2017-08-09 13:55:17.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThe 'configure_component' function would still need to be in both places, because it is called elsewhere within 'docker-install.sh'. If you wanted to share this function as well, the functions could be placed in a shared library, where both 'features' and 'docker-install.sh' could reference them.",
