        "timestamp": "2017-08-09 14:21:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI think shared library for configure component may be ideal, but worrying about impact on systems downstream, what is your take? may be can be left to a later exercise.   I think though the configure_component can be cleaned up a little bit, the JAVA_HOME, POLICY_USER, should not be of any relevance during feature installation I believe ..",
